"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Abbas Araghchi says the US attacks whenever there is a chance for a diplomatic solution. This happens as both countries blame each other for breaking ceasefires during celebrations of the Soviet Union's victory over Nazi Germany.\",            \"english_title\": \"US and Diplomatic Solutions\",            \"translated_version\": \"Abbas Araghchi dice que Estados Unidos ataca cuando hay una oportunidad para una soluci\u00f3n diplom\u00e1tica. Esto pasa mientras ambos pa\u00edses se culpan por romper treguas durante celebraciones de la victoria de la Uni\u00f3n Sovi\u00e9tica sobre la Alemania nazi.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Estados Unidos y Soluciones Diplom\u00e1ticas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A hacking group broke into the academic software Canvas, which is used by many schools and universities worldwide.\",            \"english_title\": \"Canvas Hacking Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un grupo de hackers entr\u00f3 en el software acad\u00e9mico Canvas, que es usado por muchas escuelas y universidades en todo el mundo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente de Hackeo en Canvas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"About 12 countries are linked to the hantavirus outbreak on the MV Hondius, with the UN health agency confirming at least five cases.\",            \"english_title\": \"Hantavirus Outbreak on MV Hondius\",            \"translated_version\": \"Alrededor de 12 pa\u00edses est\u00e1n relacionados con el brote de hantavirus en el MV Hondius, con la agencia de salud de la ONU confirmando al menos cinco casos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Brote de Hantavirus en MV Hondius\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Greek media report that a drone, possibly with explosives, could be Ukrainian or related to the Russia-Ukraine war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Incident in Greece\", 